    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-01-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-01-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="180" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d180">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Ford</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-01-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 20, 1868.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> Referring to the note that was addressed
                            to you by the late Sir Frederick Bruce on the 22d of December, 1865, to
                            your reply dated the <pb facs="0472" n="424" xml:id="pg_424"/> 29th of
                            that month, and to the late Sir Frederick Brace’s note of July 13, 1866,
                            I have the honor to inform you that I have received the instructions of
                            my government to endeavor to obtain an answer to the proposal made by
                            the government of Great Britain to that of the United States with regard
                            to a mutual arrangement to be entered into between the respective
                            governments for providing for the relief of destitute seamen of the two
                            nations.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, with the highest consideration, sir, your most
                            obedient humble servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FRANCIS CLARE FORD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
